import { Box, Container, Text } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import React from 'react'

const HomePage = () => {
  return (
   <Container maxW='xl' centerContent>
      <Box
      d='flex'
      justifyContent='center'
      p={3}
      bg={"white"}
      w="100%"
      m="40px 0 15px 0"
      borderRadius="lg"
      borderWidth="1px"
      >
         <Text>Bntu chat</Text>
      </Box>
      <Box></Box>
   </Container>
  )
}

export default HomePage
